responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "CBEF2C334D0111D0EE4D74B6C2FF46C7", "Slain and abducted by grave robbers. I am saddened. But I must look upon the glint of light in darkness. Now I don\'t have to share the wealth of my name. I can retake the land on my own. Provided you have the deed?")
